name: The first jumpscare video I saw
description: I remember the first time I used the Internet, I would always open a video in my facebook link or watch it randomly on youtube, as well as from my sister's phone. Yet there is a video monumental enough for me. It was a video that initially showed a bench that swayed itself in the living room. And then suddenly a scary face appeared, which made me quite shocked and scared at the time. I found out later that face was a character from one of the characters in the movie the exorcist
